Y(i,j) = \sum_{\substack{i'=0\text{ to }M-1 \\ j'=0\text{ to }M-1}} X(i-i',j-j'),
X(i,j) = Y(i,j) - \sum_{\substack{i'=0\text{ to }M-1 \\ j'=0\text{ to }M-1 \\ (i,j) \neq (0,0)}} X(i-i',j-j').
X(1,1) = Y(1,1)
